{"type":"message","id":"9ce8c2b8","parentId":"a8f81a66","timestamp":"2026-03-12T10:09:10.024Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] 你得先把 Chrome 里的目标标签页挂上 Relay。\n\n做法：\n1. 用 Chrome 打开一个标签页\n2. 点一下 OpenClaw Browser Relay 插件按钮\n3. 确认徽标变成 ON\n\n你挂好后回我一句，我就直接用 Chrome 去搜 `qwe`。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":216,"output":81,"cacheRead":29440,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":29737,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773310145522}}
