{"type":"message","id":"11ce2f1f","parentId":"93713e45","timestamp":"2026-03-12T10:11:18.593Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] 我这边直接试了两种“自带的”方式，都卡住了：\n\n1. **内置网页搜索**\n   - 缺 Brave API key\n   - 现在报的是 `missing_brave_api_key`\n\n2. **内置浏览器**\n   - 浏览器启动路径配错了\n   - 它在找：\n     `/home/node/.cache/ms-playwright/chromium-1208/chrome-linux64/chrome`\n   - 但你机器上实际看到的是：\n     `/home/node/.cache/ms-playwright/chromium-1208/chrome-linux/chrome`\n\n所以现在不是不会搜，是**环境这边还没配顺**。\n\n你要的话我可以下一步直接帮你继续查：\n- 哪个配置把 browser executablePath 写错了\n- 顺手把它改对\n- 再试一次用内置浏览器搜 `qwe`\n\n如果你愿意，我就直接开始定位这个配置。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":139,"output":212,"cacheRead":36608,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":36959,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773310269892}}
