{"type":"message","id":"c6906715","parentId":"fbdd1406","timestamp":"2026-03-12T10:13:53.438Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] 找到了，**错配位置就在主配置里**：\n\n### 错误配置位置\n文件：\n`~/.openclaw/openclaw.json`\n\n字段：\n```json\n\"browser\": {\n  \"executablePath\": \"/home/node/.cache/ms-playwright/chromium-1208/chrome-linux64/chrome\"\n}\n```\n\n### 实际存在的路径\n你机器上现在有的是：\n```bash\n/home/node/.cache/ms-playwright/chromium-1208/chrome-linux/chrome\n```\n\n也就是说，问题就是：\n- 配置里写成了 `chrome-linux64/chrome`\n- 实际目录是 `chrome-linux/chrome`\n\n---\n\n### 另外我顺手看到\n这几个备份文件里也还是同样的旧路径：\n- `~/.openclaw/openclaw.json.bak`\n- `~/.openclaw/openclaw.json.bak.1`\n\n所以主配置和备份配置都带着这个错。\n\n---\n\n### 文档里对应的配置项\nOpenClaw 官方文档也明确是这个配置项：\n\n```bash\nopenclaw config get browser.executablePath\nopenclaw config set browser.executablePath \"...\"\n```\n\n所以排查结论很明确：  \n**就是 `browser.executablePath` 配错了。**\n\n如果你要，我下一步可以直接帮你：\n1. 改 `openclaw.json`\n2. 顺手更新哈希基线\n3. 再测一次内置 browser 能不能正常起起来"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":30199,"output":522,"cacheRead":37120,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":67841,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773310419275}}
