{"type":"message","id":"b40a1912","parentId":"e6e842b2","timestamp":"2026-03-12T10:16:37.288Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] 3 件都做了，结果如下。\n\n### 1）已修正浏览器路径配置\n改了这三个文件里的 `browser.executablePath`：\n\n- `~/.openclaw/openclaw.json`\n- `~/.openclaw/openclaw.json.bak`\n- `~/.openclaw/openclaw.json.bak.1`\n\n从：\n```text\n/home/node/.cache/ms-playwright/chromium-1208/chrome-linux64/chrome\n```\n\n改成：\n```text\n/home/node/.cache/ms-playwright/chromium-1208/chrome-linux/chrome\n```\n\n---\n\n### 2）已更新哈希基线\n已刷新：\n\n- `~/.openclaw/.config-baseline.sha256`\n- `~/.openclaw/security-baselines/skill-mcp-baseline.sha256`\n\n新的配置基线哈希现在是：\n```text\n3211820e3bb20ca8cecf52349c84cf6f17b46882554e697cfc123e781e9086d6  /home/node/.openclaw/openclaw.json\n```\n\n---\n\n### 3）已验证内置 browser 能启动\n现在内置浏览器已经能正常起了，识别到的可执行文件就是修正后的路径：\n\n```text\n/home/node/.cache/ms-playwright/chromium-1208/chrome-linux/chrome\n```\n\n我也实际打开了 Google 搜索 `qwe`。\n\n---\n\n### 但 Google 这次没给正常结果页\n它直接出了风控页，提示：\n\n- `Our systems have detected unusual traffic from your computer network`\n\n也就是：\n**浏览器本身已经修好**\n但 **Google 把当前出口 IP 判成异常流量了**\n\n所以现在不是配置问题了，是 Google 那边拦了这次请求。\n\n---\n\n### 顺手补一句\n`openclaw gateway restart` 这边显示 systemd service 是 disabled，不过 RPC probe 是 ok，浏览器也已经实际能启动，所以这次不影响你刚要的修复验证。\n\n---\n\n如果你要，我下一步可以继续两种处理：\n\n1. **我去把灾备脚本第 13 段也一起改稳**\n2. **换个搜索引擎测一下内置 browser**（比如 Bing / DuckDuckGo），确认浏览链路彻底可用"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":103,"output":518,"cacheRead":71040,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":71661,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773310578234}}
